These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
5 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, goat, snake, cat
The people have 5 different jobs:  manager, designer, project-manager, chef, firefighter
1. the chef is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the chef is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
5. the firefighter is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
7. the firefighter is on the left of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Pet   | turtle | goat | ferret | cat | snake |
| Job   | firefighter    | manager | project-manager     | chef       | designer  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, farmhouse, craftsman, cottage
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, sailing, skateboarding, weightlifting, lacrosse
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the cottage house##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is in the middle##1
5. the cape-cod house is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the cottage house##1
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| House      | cape-cod | farmhouse | gothic-revival | craftsman | cottage |
| Sport   | skateboarding  | weightlifting   | swimming       | sailing    | lacrosse   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, cola, fanta, 7up
5 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony, snake, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Beverage        | cola | fanta | almond-milk | juice | 7up |
| Pet   | pony  | hedgehog      | goldfish | snake | ferret      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: malaysian, chinese, canadian, indian, egyptian
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, trance, gospel, punk, classical
1. the egyptian is on the right of the fan of trance##1
2. the canadian is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of country##1
4. the chinese is on the right of the fan of classical##1
5. the malaysian is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the fan of gospel is on the far right##1
7. the fan of classical is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Nationality   | indian    | malaysian        | canadian | chinese | egyptian |
| Music-Genre     | country | punk | classical  | trance   | gospel |

