.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, orange, lilac, purple, grey
The people have 5 different jobs:  electrician, designer, manager, teacher, chef
1. the teacher is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
2. the designer is the person who likes grey##1
3. the manager is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
4. the manager is in the middle##1
5. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
6. the chef is the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Color    | lilac   | fuchsia     | orange   | purple         | grey |
| Job   | electrician | teacher | manager | chef | designer     |

