.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
5 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, rat, guinea-pig, rabbit
House: colonial, art-deco, cape-cod, victorian, wooden
1. the victorian house is in the middle##1
2. the colonial house is on the far right##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the left of the victorian house##1
4. the cape-cod house is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the wooden house is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Pet       | guinea-pig   | rat   | lizard | rabbit | hedgehog |
| House   | art-deco | cape-cod | victorian   | wooden | colonial       |

