.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, coffee, sprite, mirinda
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, dunhill, alhambra, bluemaster, aristoff
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the alhambra-smoker is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Beverage     | hot-chocolate   | coffee  | mirinda      | lemonade | sprite     |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | alhambra | dunhill | ritmeester   | aristoff |

