.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
There are 5 different nationalities: thai, polish, canadian, nigerian, brazilian
City: venice, paris, boston, san-francisco, new-york
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the brazilian is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the thai is on the right of the polish##1
7. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Nationality     | polish | thai       | brazilian | nigerian | canadian    |
| City   | san-francisco   | new-york | boston  | paris     | venice |

