.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade, 7up
House: cottage, victorian, gothic-revival, art-deco, craftsman
1. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
5. the craftsman house is on the left of the victorian house##1
6. the person drinking 7up is the victorian house##1
7. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Beverage         | lemonade | water | hot-chocolate | 7up | soy-milk |
| House   | gothic-revival       | art-deco   | craftsman         | victorian   | cottage   |

