.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: epic, sports, fantasy, animation, comedy
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, board-games, camping, woodworking, baking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | animation | sports | fantasy | epic |
| Hobby           | baking      | board-games    | woodworking  | cooking     | camping     |

