.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, adventure, mystery, romance
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, november, october, july, march
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | animation  | adventure | scientific | romance |
| Birthday    | november    | july | march   | february       | october        |

