.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
There are 5 different nationalities: indian, argentine, russian, egyptian, australian
The people have 5 different hobbies: filmmaking, camping, puzzles, gardening, skydiving
1. the australian is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the australian is on the left of the argentine##1
4. the argentine is on the far right##1
5. the russian is on the right of the egyptian##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the argentine##1
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Nationality    | indian | egyptian          | russian    | australian | argentine  |
| Hobby   | puzzles  | skydiving | filmmaking | gardening | camping |

