.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: rock, indie, electronic, trance, techno
There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, mauve, blue, apricot, amber
1. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes mauve is the fan of rock##1
4. the fan of techno is the person who likes blue##1
5. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the fan of rock##1
6. the fan of trance is in the middle##1
7. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | rock      | trance | indie | techno |
| Color     | apricot  | mauve | aquamarine     | amber     | blue  |

