2. the person watching crime movies is in the middle##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
