.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, handball, climbing, cricket, biathlon
The people use 5 different means of transport: scooter, van, ship, roller, jet-ski
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person driving the ship is the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Sport           | cricket     | biathlon | surfing | climbing  | handball |
| Transport   | scooter | jet-ski               | van     | ship | roller |

