The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, woodworking, fishing, traveling, video-games
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is in the middle##1
6. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
7. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |  3   |    4    |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | zombie    | epic | scientific   | disaster |
| Hobby     | woodworking | board-games | traveling | fishing | video-games    |

