.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
5 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, horse, fish, lizard
The people use 5 different means of transport: ship, car, helicopter, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the bird is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Pet   | goldfish   | fish  | bird | lizard | horse  |
| Transport         | ship | helicopter | motorbike  | quad-bike    | car |

