.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
5 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit, horse, goldfish, chinchilla
The people have 5 different jobs:  project-manager, writer, lawyer, journalist, musician
1. the writer is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
3. the journalist is on the far left##1
4. the lawyer is the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the musician##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Pet   | chinchilla     | horse       | turtle     | rabbit  | goldfish  |
| Job      | journalist | project-manager | writer | musician | lawyer |

