.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, cain, chaman, davidoff, bolivar
There are 5 different nationalities: canadian, egyptian, japanese, brazilian, mexican
1. the egyptian is in the middle##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the mexican##1
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the canadian##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
5. the japanese is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Cigar   | cain | bolivar | chaman | pall-mall | davidoff |
| Nationality           | mexican | brazilian  | egyptian    | canadian  | japanese   |

 